reviewText: This is a great and cheap memory card. It is what it is.....it is compatible for Wii and gamecube its 64 MB 1019 block memory. If you need one , but it.Great product
Works great. Cheap price and way more memory than on the Nintendo make. Really great for you retro fans out there.
Works perfectly for the game cube I purchased. Came very quickly and i would buy this again when i need to.
One of the largest memory cards for the gamecube. It works great and loads fast. No need for formatting at all.

My lady dug out her kids old gamecube and games and started playing her old favorite Harvest Moon titles. She quickly discovered the memory card wasn't there anymore when she couldn't save her games. So in search I went.I was surprised to find these were still available and not too expensive. This one does the trick, has room for quite a few saves. She is happy, so I am happy.
